{
  "id": "5de7dbc8f12adc001703f101",
  "title": "視点はカメラ位置か視野中心か",
  "created": 1575476184,
  "updated": 1575524867,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5de7dbc8f12adc001703f101",
      "text": "視点はカメラ位置か視野中心か",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575476184,
      "updated": 1575476356
    },
    {
      "id": "5de7dbd7aff09e00007d9668",
      "text": "僕は「[視点]=[viewpoint]=[カメラ位置]」という認識だったが「視点=[視野中心]、[視座]=カメラ位置」という認識の人もいるということを知った",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575476184,
      "updated": 1575476373
    },
    {
      "id": "5de7dbd8aff09e00007d9669",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575476184,
      "updated": 1575476184
    },
    {
      "id": "5de7dca6aff09e00007d966a",
      "text": ">視点（してん）という言葉は、通常異なった2つの意味で用いられる。1つはどこから見ているかという、対象を見るときの[立脚点]のことであり、もう1つはどこを見ているかという、[注視点]のことである。本記事では原則として前者の意味で用いる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575476390,
      "updated": 1575476783
    },
    {
      "id": "5de7dca7aff09e00007d966c",
      "text": "\t[視点 - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%A6%96%E7%82%B9]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575476391,
      "updated": 1575476402
    },
    {
      "id": "5de7dcb2aff09e00007d966d",
      "text": "\t「どこから」「どこを」という表現が柔らかくて良い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575476402,
      "updated": 1575476420
    },
    {
      "id": "5de7dcc4aff09e00007d966e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575476420,
      "updated": 1575476420
    },
    {
      "id": "5de7dd5baff09e00007d9670",
      "text": "\t>The position from which something is observed or considered; an angle, outlook or point of view.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575476571,
      "updated": 1575476580
    },
    {
      "id": "5de7dcc4aff09e00007d966f",
      "text": "\t\thttps://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/viewpoint",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575476420,
      "updated": 1575476582
    },
    {
      "id": "5de7dca6aff09e00007d966b",
      "text": "\t>viewpoint (on something): a way of thinking about a subject",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575476390,
      "updated": 1575476665
    },
    {
      "id": "5de7ddaaaff09e00007d9672",
      "text": "\t>a direction or place from which you look at something",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575476650,
      "updated": 1575476680
    },
    {
      "id": "5de7dda9aff09e00007d9671",
      "text": "\t\thttps://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/english/viewpoint",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575476650,
      "updated": 1575476694
    },
    {
      "id": "5de7ddd6aff09e00007d9674",
      "text": "\t英語のviewpointには「どこから」の意味しかなさげ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575476694,
      "updated": 1575524867
    },
    {
      "id": "5de7dddeaff09e00007d9675",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575476702,
      "updated": 1575476702
    },
    {
      "id": "5de7de3faff09e00007d9676",
      "text": "「どこから」「どこを」を区別する思考は有益そうだが、それの「どこから」の側を表現する言葉として「どこから」にも「どこを」にも使われている単語を使うのは筋が悪い。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575476799,
      "updated": 1575477582
    },
    {
      "id": "5de7e12eaff09e00007d9687",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1575477550,
      "updated": 1575477550
    }
  ]
}